description: Victor was spotted by one of our scouts at the local skatepark.He is 21 years old and in terrific shape. He says he doesn't do anything in particular to stay in shape, just skates a lot and plays sports any chance he gets. He currently has a girlfriend, and by the looks of what's inside his pants, we have a feeling that he knows how to please.Watch Victor in three scenes. First, he relaxes with a magazine and a video in the living room. Next, he moves on to office where he scouts out the web for some pictures to keep him satisfied. And last but not least, he gets himself worked up for the grand finale in the bedroom.
title: Victor
